&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THIS POSITION&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Digital Extremes is seeking an intermediate &lt;strong&gt;Digital Artist&lt;/strong&gt; to capture high-quality in-game screenshots and promotional art for &lt;em&gt;Warframe&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Soulframe&lt;/em&gt;. This role is tailor-made for a visual storyteller who bridges the gap between virtual photography and high-end post-production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate has a proven eye for capturing marketing-ready screenshots that effectively showcase key update features, upcoming gameplay mechanics, and new in-game items. &lt;strong&gt;Deep familiarity with &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Warframe&#39;s&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Captura photomode is a significant advantage, though equivalent experience with modern in-game photomodes is highly valued.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By combining digital painting, graphic design, and expert Photoshop compositing, you will transform raw assets into polished promotional pieces that resonate with our global community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;In-Game Screenshot Capture:&lt;/strong&gt; Frame, light, and capture high-resolution marketing screenshots using Captura photomode and internal engine tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Photoshop Compositing &amp;amp; Paint-overs:&lt;/strong&gt; Utilize Adobe Photoshop to photo-bash, paint over, retouch, color grade, and add intensive post-effects to elevate raw captures into cinematic art.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Graphic Design &amp;amp; Assets:&lt;/strong&gt; Integrate marketing art with strong design elements to create promotional banners, print designs, and social media assets with a keen focus on composition, typography, and brand identity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Growth:&lt;/strong&gt; Stay adaptable. Evolve alongside our pipeline needs, which includes the gradual adoption of Maya over time for advanced 3D asset manipulation and scene posing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 3+ years of experience producing digital art, marketing screenshots, or promotional assets within the gaming industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Captura &amp;amp; Virtual Photography:&lt;/strong&gt; Demonstrated ability to capture high-end promotional screenshots. Specific expertise in Captura photomode is highly beneficial.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Advanced proficiency in Adobe Photoshop for digital compositing, photo-bashing, and matte painting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Artistic Fundamentals:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong command of graphic design principles, composition, camera angles, and cinematic lighting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; A proven track record of meeting tight production deadlines while delivering polished, digital- and print-ready assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portfolio:&lt;/strong&gt; Required. Must demonstrate a clear narrative focus through high-quality virtual photography and final, composited marketing art.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PREFERRED EXTRAS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active familiarity with the &lt;em&gt;Warframe&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Soulframe&lt;/em&gt; universes and their unique aesthetics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic familiarity with Maya or similar 3D software packages (or a strong eagerness to learn).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience organizing highly layered, complex source files (PSDs) for easy asset splitting and repurposing across various digital platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
