&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Design, develop, and maintain robust ETL/ELT pipelines for data ingestion and processing from varied, complex data sources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Governance &amp;amp; Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure infrastructure and pipelines strictly comply with government policies, data privacy standards, and GDPR regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
